<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="faq" id="faq">
  <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:48px">
    <div class="section-label">FAQ</div>
    <div class="section-title">Frequently asked questions</div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">What is AgencyMCP?</button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">AgencyMCP is a remote MCP server that connects Claude (by Anthropic) to your marketing platforms — Google Ads, Meta Ads, GA4, Search Console, and Sheets. It gives Claude 350+ real API tools to manage your accounts, run audits, create campaigns, and generate reports.</div></div></div>

  <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">How does it connect to my ad accounts?</button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">You authenticate with Google and/or Meta via OAuth. Your encrypted refresh tokens are stored securely. When Claude makes a tool call, we use your tokens to call the platform APIs on your behalf. You can revoke access anytime.</div></div></div>

  <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">Is my data safe?</button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">Yes. All OAuth tokens are encrypted with Fernet (AES-128). Each user has isolated credentials. We never store your ad data — we just proxy API calls. JWT auth with session tracking prevents unauthorized access.</div></div></div>

  <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">What can Claude actually do with this?</button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">Everything you'd do in the platform UIs: pull performance reports, find wasted spend, optimize bids, create campaigns, manage keywords, build audiences, run GA4 cohort analyses, check GSC rankings, update spreadsheets — and more.</div></div></div>

  <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">Do I need Claude Pro?</button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">AgencyMCP works with both Claude.ai (free and Pro) and Claude Desktop. You do need an MCP-capable Claude plan that supports custom integrations. Claude Pro is recommended for the best experience.</div></div></div>

  <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">Can I use this for my agency clients?</button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">Absolutely. The agency tools let you manage multiple accounts, run bulk audits, and generate cross-client reports. Each client's credentials are isolated and secure.</div></div></div>

  <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">What happens after the free trial?</button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">After 14 days, you'll need the Pro plan ($99/month) to continue using the tools. No auto-charge — you decide when to upgrade. Your connected accounts and data stay intact.</div></div></div>
</section>

